chara_2013 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_list.xlsx", sheet = "2013")
chara_2014 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_list.xlsx", sheet = "2014")
chara_2015 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_list.xlsx", sheet = "2015")
chara_2016 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_list.xlsx", sheet = "2016")
chara_2017 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_list.xlsx", sheet = "2017")
chara_2018 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_list.xlsx", sheet = "2018")

data_2013 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_data.xlsx", sheet = "chara_2013") %>% mutate(MID=paste0("2013_",MID))
data_2014 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_data.xlsx", sheet = "chara_2014") %>% mutate(MID=paste0("2014_",MID))
data_2015 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_data.xlsx", sheet = "chara_2015") %>% mutate(MID=paste0("2015_",MID))
data_2016 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_data.xlsx", sheet = "chara_2016") %>% mutate(MID=paste0("2016_",MID))
data_2017 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_data.xlsx", sheet = "chara_2017") %>% mutate(MID=paste0("2017_",MID))
data_2018 <- openxlsx::read.xlsx("./data/chara_data.xlsx", sheet = "chara_2018") %>% mutate(MID=paste0("2018_",MID))

colnames(data_2013) <- chara_2013$
colnames(data_2014) <- chara_2014$
colnames(data_2015) <- chara_2015$
colnames(data_2016) <- chara_2016$
colnames(data_2017) <- chara_2017$
colnames(data_2018) <- chara_2018$

participant_2013 <- data_2013 %>% count(MID, M_SEX, M_AGE) %>%
  mutate(Generation=case_when(
    M_AGE<10 ~ "0s",
    M_AGE >= 10 & M_AGE <20 ~ "10s",
    M_AGE >= 20 & M_AGE <30 ~ "20s",
    M_AGE >= 30 & M_AGE <40 ~ "30s",
    M_AGE >= 40 & M_AGE <50 ~ "40s",
    M_AGE >= 50 ~ "50s"
  )) %>% select(-n)
participant_2014 <- data_2014 %>% count(MID, M_SEX, M_AGE) %>%
  mutate(Generation=case_when(
    M_AGE<10 ~ "0s",
    M_AGE >= 10 & M_AGE <20 ~ "10s",
    M_AGE >= 20 & M_AGE <30 ~ "20s",
    M_AGE >= 30 & M_AGE <40 ~ "30s",
    M_AGE >= 40 & M_AGE <50 ~ "40s",
    M_AGE >= 50 ~ "50s"
  )) %>% select(-n)
participant_2015 <- data_2015 %>% count(MID, M_SEX, M_AGE) %>%
  mutate(Generation=case_when(
    M_AGE<10 ~ "0s",

2013

data_2013_1 <- data_2013 %>%
  gather(key =  Q, value = A_0, -c(MID, M_SEX, M_AGE)) %>%
  merge(
    chara_2013 %>% rename(Q=),
    by = "Q", all.x = T
  ) %>%
  filter(=="") %>%
  mutate(
    A=case_when(
      A_0 == 1 ~ "",
      A_0 == 2 ~ "",
      A_0 == 3 ~ "",
      A_0 == 4 ~ ""
    )
  ) %>%
  count(MID, , Q, A) %>%
  spread(A, n) %>%
  select(MID, , Q, , , , )

data_2013_3 <- data_2013 %>%
  gather(key =  Q, value = A, -c(MID, M_SEX, M_AGE)) %>%
  merge(
    chara_2013 %>% rename(Q=),
    by="Q", all.x = T
  ) %>%
  filter(=="" & !="") %>%
  count(MID, , Q, A)

data_2013_4 <- data_2013 %>%
  gather(key =  Q, value = A, -c(MID, M_SEX, M_AGE)) %>%
  merge(
    chara_2013 %>% rename(Q=),
    by="Q", all.x = T
  ) %>%
  filter(=="" & !="") %>%
  count(MID, , Q, A)

total_2013_ <- participant_2013 %>%
  merge(
    data_2013_1,
    by="MID", all=T
  ) %>%
# data_2013_1 %>%
  # select(MID, , ) %>%
  merge(
    data_2013_3 %>% rename(=A) %>%
      select(MID, , ),
    by=c("MID", ""), all=T
  ) %>%
  merge(
    data_2013_4 %>% rename(=A) %>%
      select(MID, , ),
    by=c("MID", ""), all=T
  )
rm(data_2013_1, data_2013_3, data_2013_4)
total_2013_ %>%
  rename(Character=) %>%
  replace_na(list(=0, =0, =0, =0, =0)) %>%
  group_by(Character) %>%
  # count()
  summarise(
    Popular = count(data_2013)$n - sum(),
    Like = sum(),
    Dislike = sum(),
    Own = sum(),
    Wish = sum()
  ) %>%
  mutate( Total = Like - Dislike + Own + Wish ) %>%
  mutate( Score_1 = Total / Popular ) %>%
  mutate( Score_2 = Total / Like ) %>%
  # arrange(desc(Popular))
  # arrange(Total)
  arrange(desc(Score_2))

  count(MID, , Q, A)

total_2018_ <- participant_2018 %>%
  merge(
    data_2018_1,
    by="MID", all.x=T
  ) %>%

total_2018_ %>%
  rename(Character=) %>%
  replace_na(list(=0, =0, =0, =0, =0, =0, =0)) %>%
  group_by(Character) %>%
  # count()
  summarise(
    N = n(),
    Popular = N - sum(),
    Like = sum() + sum(),
    Dislike = sum() + sum(),
    Own = sum(),
    Wish = sum()
  ) %>%
  mutate( Total = Like - Dislike + Own + Wish ) %>%
  mutate( Score_1 = Total / Popular ) %>%
  mutate( Score_2 = Total / Like ) %>%
  # arrange(desc(Popular))
  # arrange(Total)
  arrange(desc(Score_2))

total_2013_15 <- rbind(total_2013_, total_2014_, total_2015_) %>%
  rename(Character=) %>%
  replace_na(list(=0, =0, =0, =0, =0, =0)) %>%
  group_by(Character) %>%
  summarise(
    N = n(),
    Popular = N - sum(),
    Like = sum(),
    Dislike = sum(),
    Neither = sum(),
    Own = sum(),
    Wish = sum()
  ) %>%
  mutate( Total = Like + Dislike + Neither + Own + Wish ) %>%
  mutate( Score_3 = (Own - Wish) / Popular ) %>%
  mutate( Score_4 = (Own - Wish) / Like ) %>%
  arrange(desc(Score_4))

# total_2013_15_2 <- total_2013_15 %>% select(Popular, Like, Dislike, Own, Wish) %>% data.frame()
total_2013_15_2 <- total_2013_15 %>% select(Like, Dislike, Own, Wish) %>% data.frame()
rownames(total_2013_15_2) <- total_2013_15$Character
# total_2016_18_2 <- total_2016_18 %>% select(Popular, Like, Dislike, Own, Wish) %>% data.frame()
total_2016_18_2 <- total_2016_18 %>% select(Like, Dislike, Own, Wish) %>% data.frame()
rownames(total_2016_18_2) <- total_2016_18$Character

data_kmeans_1 <- total_2013_15_2 %>% kmeans(3)
data_kmeans_2 <- total_2016_18_2 %>% kmeans(3)

cls <- data_kmeans_1$cluster %>% data.frame()
total_2013_15$cluster <- as.character(cls$.)
cls <- data_kmeans_2$cluster %>% data.frame()
total_2016_18$cluster <- as.character(cls$.)

ggplot() +
  geom_point(data=total_2013_15, aes(x=Popular, y=Wish, colour=cluster)) +
  ggrepel::geom_label_repel(data=total_2013_15 %>% filter(Character==""), aes(x=Popular, y=Wish, label=Character), family="IPAGothic") +
  ggtitle(" x  2013 - 2015") +
  theme_bw() + theme(text = element_text(family = "IPAGothic"))
